PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for the Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency of Gregory MacKenzie, of Sydney, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Barry Martin, whose term has expired.
